Package: rcompendium
Title: Generic R Compendium Template
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Barry", family = "Brook", role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: A reproducible, generic R compendium template using 'renv',
    'targets', and 'Quarto'. It is structured as an R package so it can be
    loaded with 'devtools' or 'pkgload' and used in a 'targets' pipeline.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.5)
